♪Embracing in joy♪

678
00:33:54,410 --> 00:33:58,510
♪You fill my heart; you are my shore♪

679
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:02,540
♪The world shines; love softly blooms♪

680
00:34:02,970 --> 00:34:06,850
♪Memories drift in radiant hues♪

681
