♪You fill my heart; you are my shore♪

683
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:20,920
♪I wrap you in the romance of the sky♪

684
00:34:21,160 --> 00:34:25,290
♪Let's forget about the past
and focus on the future♪

685
00:34:25,580 --> 00:34:30,070
♪Let's take the journey
into the world's cycle♪

686
00:34:44,700 --> 00:34:47,220
We were all set to move
into the side chamber tonight

687
00:34:47,220 --> 00:34:49,300
and even packed everything up.

688
00:34:50,580 --> 00:34:53,260
But the Lord felt sorry for the Lady

689
00:34:53,660 --> 00:34:55,500
and insisted we stay here.

690
00:34:57,020 --> 00:34:57,860
My Lady.

691
00:34:58,260 --> 00:34:59,220
Your cheeks

692
00:34:59,220 --> 00:35:01,060
are red like fruit.

693
00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:03,100
Have you caught a chill?

694
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:05,540
I'm fine.

695
00:35:07,020 --> 00:35:08,420
However,

696
00:35:08,630 --> 00:35:10,700
my heart's been fluttery lately

697
00:35:10,700 --> 00:35:12,020
for no reason.

698
00:35:13,700 --> 00:35:14,780
Sure.

699
00:35:15,420 --> 00:35:17,980
The Lord carried you all the way back,

700
00:35:17,980 --> 00:35:19,540
and you bumped into many people.

701
00:35:20,130 --> 00:35:21,300
Who wouldn't feel flustered?

702
00:35:22,700 --> 00:35:24,020
But

703
00:35:24,370 --> 00:35:25,900
that day was worse.

704
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:28,460
That day?

705
00:35:29,900 --> 00:35:31,460
The day we entered the city.

706
00:35:31,820 --> 00:35:33,620
You had a high fever,

707
00:35:33,980 --> 00:35:36,260
and the Lord carried you back
the same way.

708
00:35:37,300 --> 00:35:39,180
He's gotten used to carrying you,

709
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:41,860
but now you're getting embarrassed.

710
00:36:15,380 --> 00:36:17,380
I misunderstood him back then.

711
00:36:18,340 --> 00:36:19,860
Leaving me outside the city

712
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:21,180
wasn't his intention.

713
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:22,460
Yet I blamed him

714
00:36:22,460 --> 00:36:24,460
and made him stay
in the side chamber for days.

715
00:36:25,820 --> 00:36:26,980
Has the Lady fallen asleep?

716
00:36:27,420 --> 00:36:28,380
Tan?

717
00:36:29,060 --> 00:36:30,140
Why is he here

718
00:36:30,140 --> 00:36:31,220
so late?

719
00:36:31,500 --> 00:36:32,420
Coming.

720
00:36:37,660 --> 00:36:38,500
My Lady.

721
00:36:39,780 --> 00:36:40,700
What's this?

722
00:36:41,180 --> 00:36:43,380
The Lord asked me to bring this.

723
00:36:43,380 --> 00:36:45,340
He said your clothes
got soaked in the rain

724
00:36:45,340 --> 00:36:46,300
outside the city.

725
00:36:46,300 --> 00:36:47,480
These are for making new ones.

726
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:50,020
He also said

727
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:51,700
you're still in mourning,

728
00:36:51,700 --> 00:36:54,020
so light-colored fabric is best.

729
00:36:56,580 --> 00:36:58,020
The Lord is very thoughtful.

730
00:37:02,740 --> 00:37:05,300
(Wei Mansion)

731
00:37:11,580 --> 00:37:12,820
She's finally here.

732
00:37:12,820 --> 00:37:14,260
Is she planning to move in now?

733
00:37:14,260 --> 00:37:15,820
The Lord stays in the side chamber,

734
00:37:15,820 --> 00:37:17,660
while she takes over the main chamber.

735
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:19,980
As a new bride,

736
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:21,260
where are her manners?

737
00:37:28,460 --> 00:37:29,350
It's still early.

738
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,300
Why are you here?

739
00:37:30,820 --> 00:37:31,820
It's cold.

740
00:37:32,300 --> 00:37:33,900
I brought your cloak.

741
00:37:57,180 --> 00:37:58,380
I don't need your care.

742
00:37:58,820 --> 00:38:00,140
Just take care of yourself.

743
00:38:22,740 --> 00:38:25,700
Is this the room prepared for the Lady?

744
00:38:26,020 --> 00:38:27,980
This is too plain.

745
00:38:28,540 --> 00:38:29,700
I didn't expect

746
00:38:29,700 --> 00:38:31,380
the Lord to treat her so well.

747
00:38:31,380 --> 00:38:33,300
Who knows what tricks she's used?

748
00:38:34,180 --> 00:38:35,180
Can you hear us there?

749
00:38:35,700 --> 00:38:37,140
Come in and let's chat.

750
00:38:38,700 --> 00:38:39,660
You're leaving?

751
00:38:41,860 --> 00:38:43,300
Back at your parents' house,

752
00:38:44,180 --> 00:38:46,580
they know you'll marry off
sooner or later,

753
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:48,300
so they treat you like an outsider.

754
00:38:49,100 --> 00:38:50,300
After you marry,

755
00:38:50,420 --> 00:38:52,640
your husband's family
also treats you like an outsider

756
00:38:53,020 --> 00:38:54,700
because you join them halfway.

757
00:38:56,820 --> 00:38:58,140
It's hard

758
00:38:58,370 --> 00:38:59,580
being a woman.

759
00:38:59,820 --> 00:39:01,220
But you're lucky.

760
00:39:01,860 --> 00:39:03,300
The Lord cherishes you.

761
00:39:03,780 --> 00:39:05,100
It's not all hardship.

762
00:39:05,340 --> 00:39:08,020
The Lord sees me as his wife
and treats me well.

763
00:39:09,540 --> 00:39:11,940
I should make sure
everything else is in order.

764
00:39:12,900 --> 00:39:15,180
Clean up this room,

765
00:39:15,460 --> 00:39:16,740
so it's more comfortable for him.

766
00:39:17,860 --> 00:39:18,700
Wait.

767
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:23,140
Since they see me as an outsider,

768
00:39:23,660 --> 00:39:25,540
then things like preparing his room

769
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:27,740
should be handled by themselves.

770
00:39:28,340 --> 00:39:29,260
Call them over.

771
00:39:30,300 --> 00:39:31,140
Yes.

772
00:39:43,860 --> 00:39:44,700
Xiaotao,

773
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:47,060
go and make some inquiries.

774
00:39:47,060 --> 00:39:47,900
Sure.

775
00:39:49,300 --> 00:39:50,140
Duang.

776
00:39:51,100 --> 00:39:51,940
What do you want?

777
00:39:52,180 --> 00:39:53,500
I have a few questions.

778
00:39:54,320 --> 00:39:54,940
The Advisor said

779
00:39:54,940 --> 00:39:56,420
no questions about military affairs,

780
00:39:56,420 --> 00:39:57,740
no questions about state affairs,

781
00:39:57,740 --> 00:39:59,020
and no questions about the Lord.

782
00:39:59,020 --> 00:39:59,860
Sure.

783
00:39:59,860 --> 00:40:01,220
I'm not asking about the Lord.

784
00:40:01,220 --> 00:40:02,340
I'm asking about you.

785
00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:03,420
Me?

786
00:40:03,420 --> 00:40:04,260
What about me?

787
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:06,260
I care about you.

788
00:40:07,100 --> 00:40:07,940
Then go ahead.

789
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:09,140
Let me ask you.

790
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:12,020
How do you normally get along
with the Lord?

791
00:40:12,340 --> 00:40:13,580
We eat and sleep together.

792
00:40:14,380 --> 00:40:16,940
What do you usually do?

793
00:40:17,420 --> 00:40:19,100
We're always training.

794
00:40:19,380 --> 00:40:20,220
That's good.

795
00:40:20,420 --> 00:40:21,500
After training,

796
00:40:21,660 --> 00:40:22,540
what do you eat?

797
00:40:23,660 --> 00:40:24,660
Lots of stuff.

798
00:40:24,660 --> 00:40:26,260
Beef.

799
00:40:26,260 --> 00:40:27,140
Lamb.

800
00:40:27,140 --> 00:40:27,980
And...

801
00:40:28,220 --> 00:40:29,580
Why am I telling you this?

802
00:40:29,940 --> 00:40:31,020
I've got serious work to do.

803
00:40:31,580 --> 00:40:33,220
I'm not done, Duang.

804
00:40:44,540 --> 00:40:45,380
What are you doing?

805
00:40:46,180 --> 00:40:47,920
Have you lost your soul
after this morning?

806
00:40:48,260 --> 00:40:49,100
No.

807
00:40:49,500 --> 00:40:50,740
I have some questions.

808
00:40:50,740 --> 00:40:51,580
Well.

809
00:40:52,020 --> 00:40:53,700
If a woman

810
00:40:53,700 --> 00:40:55,540
keeps asking you questions

811
00:40:55,780 --> 00:40:58,540
all about daily, trivial stuff,

812
00:40:58,540 --> 00:40:59,500
what is she up to?

813
00:40:59,500 --> 00:41:00,820
She's spying on military affairs.

814
00:41:00,860 --> 00:41:01,900
She wants your salary.

815
00:41:01,900 --> 00:41:02,820
Nonsense.

816
00:41:05,860 --> 00:41:07,300
You deal with women all the time.

817
00:41:07,300 --> 00:41:08,420
What do you think?

818
00:41:09,700 --> 00:41:10,740
Do you really want to know?

819
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:14,780
I'm meeting the guys tonight
at Luozhong Tavern.

820
00:41:14,780 --> 00:41:15,980
What about my wine bill?

821
00:41:15,980 --> 00:41:17,580
Fine, I'll cover it.

822
00:41:17,580 --> 00:41:18,440
Look.

823
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:19,900
I knew this would cost you.

824
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:22,220
Listen.

825
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:24,540
In this big world,

826
00:41:24,740 --> 00:41:25,980
if a man

827
00:41:26,420 --> 00:41:27,300
or a woman suddenly

828
00:41:27,300 --> 00:41:29,980
takes an interest
in someone's everyday life,

829
00:41:29,980 --> 00:41:32,420
even their food and daily schedule,

830
00:41:33,140 --> 00:41:34,060
there's no doubt

831
00:41:35,420 --> 00:41:36,820
that he or she has fallen for them.

832
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:37,780
No way.

833
00:41:37,780 --> 00:41:38,900
Absolutely not.

834
00:42:05,580 --> 00:42:06,420
My Lady,

835
00:42:07,020 --> 00:42:09,020
I asked Wei Liang in detail.

836
00:42:09,620 --> 00:42:11,400
The Lord eats and lives with them.

837
00:42:11,400 --> 00:42:12,700
So, whatever Wei Liang often eats

838
00:42:12,700 --> 00:42:15,420
(Apricots, sliced liver, red bean soup)
must be what the Lord likes.

839
00:42:15,440 --> 00:42:16,380
Then prepare these.

840
00:42:16,380 --> 00:42:17,220
Got it.

841
00:42:38,460 --> 00:42:39,300
Tan.

842
00:42:42,740 --> 00:42:43,580
Yes?

843
00:42:44,300 --> 00:42:45,620
Who arranged all this?

844
00:42:45,740 --> 00:42:46,380
It was the Lady.

845
00:42:46,380 --> 00:42:47,680
She started preparing everything

846
00:42:47,680 --> 00:42:49,040
right after you left this morning.

847
00:42:55,060 --> 00:42:56,140
Then go tell her.

848
00:42:56,700 --> 00:42:58,380
She's been in Yujun for a while.

849
00:42:59,020 --> 00:42:59,900
Tomorrow,

850
00:43:00,260 --> 00:43:01,680
I'll take her to visit Grandmother.

851
00:43:02,660 --> 00:43:03,500
Yes.

852
00:43:17,860 --> 00:43:18,700
How is it?

853
00:43:19,980 --> 00:43:21,300
It's wonderful.

854
00:43:21,740 --> 00:43:22,860
You're beautiful.

855
00:43:22,860 --> 00:43:24,700
Lady Xu will surely be pleased.

856
00:43:28,500 --> 00:43:30,500
You've always been poised
since you came of age.

857
00:43:30,500 --> 00:43:32,640
It's been a long time
since I've seen you so nervous.

858
00:43:33,420 --> 00:43:34,920
When I first came to Yujun,

859
00:43:34,940 --> 00:43:36,940
because of the relationship
between our families,

860
