as your legs are short.

876
00:44:47,040 --> 00:44:48,860
If you've gone
for an incense stick of time,

877
00:44:48,860 --> 00:44:50,100
I can still catch up with you.

878
00:44:50,180 --> 00:44:51,020
Hurry up.

879
00:45:56,923 --> 00:45:59,753
