893
00:46:55,233 --> 00:46:57,163
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

894
00:46:57,703 --> 00:47:02,623
♪How could I ever forget♪

895
00:47:03,203 --> 00:47:05,483
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

896
